{"tid":414455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣行政院長賴清德： 我主張台獨！兩岸是互不隸屬的關係","createTime":"2017-09-26T08:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T23:38:03.000Z","uid":35790,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6edd8952ca8f137b408ceba8db9262f21a18fb4e","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"無論擔任哪項職務都不會變 賴清德：我主張台獨！<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-26 12:31<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕行政院長賴清德，今日在立法院接受親民黨立委陳怡潔、國民黨立委王惠美等人的質詢，過程中被問到兩岸立場時，賴清德指出他是「主張台灣獨立的政治工作者」，不管他擔任哪個職務都不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">賴清德在回答陳怡潔的兩岸問題質詢時，表示台灣是主權獨立國家，名字叫做中華民國，兩岸則是互不隸屬的關係。</span></span>至於賴的兩岸立場為何？賴清德回應，遵循總統指示，兩岸要互助互惠，善意和承諾不變，且在不對任何壓力屈服的狀況下，推動各種工作。<br />\n<br />\n賴清德強調，兩岸有共同目標和共同敵人，應該要相互合作。他所謂的共同敵人，包括颱風、地震和愛滋病等等，增進兩岸人民福祉是共同目標，假如中國當局能理解這點，他相信許多事都能解決。<br />\n<br />\n陳怡潔則質疑，中國國台辦對賴清德沒有太多期待，賴清德對此指出，台灣是主權獨立國家，要追求的是人民最高福祉，不用侷限在強權畫的小圈子裡打轉，也不必在乎某些人的話。<br />\n<br />\n到了國民黨立委王惠美質詢兩岸立場時，賴清德說，他是1個主張台灣獨立的政治工作者，他也曾經在台南市議會講過，不管他擔任哪個職務，這個都不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n王惠美聞言後，則質問賴清德過去「親中愛台」的言論如何解釋？王惠美說，之前賴清德擔任地方首長還能隨便說說，今天已經是最高行政首長，必須要有清楚的中心思想，別害死台商。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賴清德對此強調，親中愛台和台獨主張並不違背，所謂「親中愛台」是以台灣為核心，對中國表達親善的態度，伸出友誼的手，以交流達到了解、理解、和解、諒解，所以和台獨是並行不悖的</span>。<br />\n（更新時間：16:06）<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"6965aef992693f4e84f06db34e104fa016bd781f","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104b2223bcbff60d502a03198085c991c05b3f6e","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31970336fbab00855ae6847f6a9616ebce82b4b6","tid":414455,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"好清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c512ffc960c0a8c7ceb240eda246b3cc3e21cb8c","tid":414455,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"我發現台灣人玩政治仲勁撚過香港果班<br />\n香港果班只係識屈鬼＿"},{"pid":"fd133961dd49cddd22e40f476380e68e6e31c163","tid":414455,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發現台灣人玩政治仲勁撚過香港果班<br />\n香港果班只係識屈鬼＿</blockquote><br />\n民主回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08567f5afe29952eff5c7f00fbecb6083faca929","tid":414455,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"1be990475acfa08e694f5a500435cf207f01ffc0","tid":414455,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7d9f081c8de514a147901dc47452292bd1f0f7","tid":414455,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a558d9876450fa683793afeb86b8482c418e80","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"賴清德：我是務實台獨主義者　不需另行宣布台灣獨立<br />\n<br />\n2017/09/26 16:16&nbsp;41144<br />\n<br />\n行政院長賴清德今首度到立法院施政報告並備詢，藍委蔣萬安和李彥秀採兩人一組聯合質詢模式，蔣萬安問說，兩岸關係應該比較像是情侶、夫妻、兄弟、朋友還是其他？賴清德回應說，關係是雙方的，台灣目前最重要的目的就是壯大自己，藉此同時也應該向中國北京當局伸出友誼的手，但也要看他們怎麼回應，正如蔡英文總統所說，對中國的善意和誠意不會改變，但不能在屈服下前進。<br />\n<br />\n賴清德重申，台灣是主權獨立的國家，名字叫做中華民國，兩岸之間並不隸屬。至於兩岸之間屬於哪一種關係？賴清德認為，從前總統陳水扁、馬英九到現任總統蔡英文的就職演說，都代表了台灣社會向中國釋出善意，但也是要看中國怎麼回應。藍委李彥秀問說，民進黨送到立法院的優先法案有《公民投票法》，是否支持《公投法》納入領土變更辦法？賴清德說，法案送到立法院了，尊重立院的決定，他是主張台灣獨立的政治工作者，但也是務實的台獨主義者，所謂務實就是已經是主權獨立國家，不需另行宣布台灣獨立，未來台灣前途會經過2300萬人民決定。<br />\n（余祥／台北報導）<br />\n&lt;台灣蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"7c35b8db6c8292831bd170fb2ef824107d80e328","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"他是主張台灣獨立的政治工作者，但也是務實的台獨主義者，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所謂務實就是已經是主權獨立國家，不需另行宣布台灣獨立，未來台灣前途會經過2300萬人民決定。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a0aa2c9f952f8df5edde437256cf4ebc703229f","tid":414455,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他是主張台灣獨立的政治工作者，但也是務實的台獨主義者，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所謂務實就是已經是主權獨立國家，不需另行宣布台灣獨立，未來台灣前途會經過2300萬人民決定。</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6ce509f335e103ce3f0aadefe5abe732adbf29","tid":414455,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發現台灣人玩政治仲勁撚過香港果班<br />\n香港果班只係識屈鬼＿</blockquote><br />\n台灣果啲叻可以好叻（通常都係綠營），屎都可以好屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣都有啲凈係識問人肚臍英文係咩既議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495bdb1531a8fc3ebb589111f7d79c0a4b3a20a2","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"換咗行政院長<br />\n民進黨正式全面執政<br />\n睇蔡英文係咪空心菜？"},{"pid":"4e074a6dcf85b8804feacc34a8b724ee9094629f","tid":414455,"uid":71257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:41:17.000Z","msg":"中華民國真中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和國收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f6c7ec7ccef5e97c88f0145dded43736e24279","tid":414455,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ad2e14f2c59b0645c5d3b89a50c8818b978415","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">賴清德在回答陳怡潔的兩岸問題質詢時，表示台灣是主權獨立國家，名字叫做中華民國，兩岸則是互不隸屬的關係。</span></span>至於賴的兩岸立場為何？賴清德回應，遵循總統指示，兩岸要互助互惠，善意和承諾不變，且在不對任何壓力屈服的狀況下，推動各種工作。<br />\n<br />\n華獨<br />\n借殼上市"},{"pid":"8e0cf1b78f67f9a91b17e0865742dee6dfb701ca","tid":414455,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">賴清德在回答陳怡潔的兩岸問題質詢時，表示台灣是主權獨立國家，名字叫做中華民國，兩岸則是互不隸屬的關係。</span></span>至於賴的兩岸立場為何？賴清德回應，遵循總統指示，兩岸要互助互惠，善意和承諾不變，且在不對任何壓力屈服的狀況下，推動各種工作。<br />\n<br />\n華獨<br />\n借殼上市</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係咁講<br />\n<br />\n係你班連登仔左屌又屌"},{"pid":"78ffc203c23aa8560de0a5044e57c3ece653f802","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"賴清德：台灣已是主權獨立國家 不必另行宣布獨立<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-26 17:05聯合報 記者許家瑜╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n行政院長賴清德今天首度在立法院報告施政方針及備詢，因賴曾在台南市長任內多次表達台獨主張，國民黨立委蔣萬安、李彥秀質詢時猛攻敏感兩岸問題，除了要求院長比擬兩岸目前關係，也提問是否將領土變更納入公投法。<br />\n<br />\n蔣萬安詢問賴清德，目前兩岸關係是男女、情侶、兄弟或朋友關係，哪一種類別比喻比較恰當？賴清德一開始說，「因為兩岸並不互相隸屬，關係是雙方」，但後來又改口說「台灣應該伸出友誼的橄欖枝，有自信地跟其他國家做朋友，跟北京當局、對岸亦是如此」。他說，從歷任總統的就職演說也可看出台灣善意，台灣是主權獨立的國家，他目前工作是壯大台灣，立場不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n李彥秀質問，賴清德曾多次主張「親中愛台及台獨」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">這次公投法修正草案也被行政院列為重大優先法案，是否贊成將「領土變更」連同公投法一起修正？賴清德未做正面回應，僅說「尊重立法院決定」</span></span>，但馬上被李彥秀批評「不要閃躲問題」。<br />\n<br />\n李彥秀表示，賴院長是未來最有政治實力的明星，全國人民都在觀察，如果未來挑戰總統大位，勢必要回答這個問題，「國民黨不能每次都當民進黨煞車皮」。<br />\n<br />\n賴重申，他是主張台灣獨立的政治工作者，不過，台灣已是主權獨立的國家，不必另行宣布獨立，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於台灣領土變更與否，應該交由全體人民決定</span></span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/11515/2723953?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11515%2F2723953%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5e0657af\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/11515/2723953?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"9bf7c7e452e8f30ff1943bf0681523987907d139","tid":414455,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a2937f0f5c93aeb7fdc2bb9a2232ddb63329681","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a1a5609599bbea104dd2cde2bf854ceff850c6","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39033fd37d34aaff1e5e9485a78a820fc501b114","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5a3ce8293d5e828e1b5a8bacf0aa1736357d58","tid":414455,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"中華民國萬歲🇹🇼"},{"pid":"9951c5c6314c2d240e5519ae2c2a9be57f6551ea","tid":414455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}